    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5103655/" class="title-link">应与梁氏译注《英国文学选》一同参读！</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5103655"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1094056/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1094056-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1094056/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">砺剑阁主</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
